    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skills",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/10316b5178d5109d597f415d6e7903dc_6194548844514394894.png",
                "id": "talent78537",
                "key": "Schematic Setup ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Schematic Setup "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>, creates 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burst Scan</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Burst Scan</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Before either side chooses their action:</span> If your side has Dendro Core or Bountiful Core, -1 to their <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s)</span>, and <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Discard</span> the card at the top of your deck. After this, deal <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span> equal to the original Elemental Dice Cost of the card you <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Discard</span>ed.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">(s): 1</span> (Can stack. Max 3 stacks)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/5939d61b0bbbc9069caa164fbf967189_928274352603365328.png",
                "id": "talent10187",
                "key": "Artistic Ingenuity",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Artistic Ingenuity"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>. This character gains <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Mehrak's Assistance</span>, creating 2 stacks of <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burst Scan</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Mehrak's Assistance</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br>The character's Normal Attacks deal +1 DMG, and the <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span> they deal is converted to <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>. <br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After the character uses a Normal Attack:</span> Create a <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burst Scan</span>.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Duration (Rounds): 2</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Burst Scan</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Before either side chooses their action:</span> If your side has Dendro Core or Bountiful Core, -1 to their <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s)</span>, and <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Discard</span> the card at the top of your deck. After this, deal <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span> equal to the original Elemental Dice Cost of the card you <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Discard</span>ed.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 1</span> (Can stack. Max 3 stacks)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/23c5b1ed3865c0fe1cc2409747bb043a_5153061803837000927.png",
                "id": "talent78643",
                "key": "Painted Dome",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Painted Dome"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Dendro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bloom</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] that grants +2 DMG to the next instance of Pyro or Electro DMG</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] that will deal 1 Pyro DMG at the end of the Round (Takes effect once, max 2 stacks)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] that grants +1 DMG to the next 2 instances of Dendro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_1948108260169870444.png",
                "id": "talent80538",
                "key": "Dendro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Dendro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Physical DMG</span></strong><br>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage</span> of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages</span> remaining.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Discard</span></strong><br>Use Action Cards or Character Skill effects to Discard Action Cards from Hand or Deck.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Duration (Rounds)</span></strong><br>Each time you reach the end of a Round, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds)</span> -1.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds)</span> runs out.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_581501371857904414.png",
                "id": "talent95879",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detailed Rules"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
